{"article_id":"7GL7XV2TYadvmR1b","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump took a victory lap on the economy Tuesday night in his first State of the Union address ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"declaring","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that his tax cuts have sparked an American revival ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and reaching out to Democrats","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to work on problems from immigration to infrastructure .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" This is our new American moment , \"","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Trump told Congress in a prime-time address .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"\" There has never been a better time","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"to start living the American dream . \"","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"After a turbulent first year","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"in which he often clashed with congressional Democrats ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Mr. Trump appealed to liberal lawmakers to compromise on issues such as his major proposal on immigration and border security","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"- providing a path to citizenship for 1.8 million illegal immigrant \" Dreamers , \"","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"spending $ 25 billion","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to build a border wall","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and enacting other immigration restrictions .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Failure","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to reach a deal","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"could prompt a partial government shutdown next week .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"\" Struggling communities , especially immigrant communities , will also be helped by immigration policies","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that focus on the best interests of American workers and American families , \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" So tonight I am extending an open hand","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"to work with members of both parties , Democrats and Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to protect our citizens , of every background , color , and creed . \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The president also announced","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"he has signed an executive order","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that will keep open the high-security military detention center at Guantanamo Bay , Cuba","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"- reversing a decision by President Barack Obama in 2009","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"to close the prison .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Gitmo is still open , with 41 alleged terrorist detainees ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"because Congress refused to go along with Mr. Obama ' s order .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"As part of that order , Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"he is directing Defense Secretary James Mattis to reexamine U.S. military detention policy .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"In a long-awaited move , Mr. Trump outlined a $ 1.5 trillion plan","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"to rebuild the nation ' s crumbling bridges and roads ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"using $ 200 billion in federal spending over a decade","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to spur more funding from state and local governments and private enterprise .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" I am asking both parties to come together","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to give us the safe , fast , reliable , and modern infrastructure","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"our economy needs","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and our people deserve , \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"the president said .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Aides said","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Mr. Trump wanted to \" speak from the heart \" about his vision for a thriving economy","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"lifting up all citizens .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Earlier in the day , the president told journalists at the White House","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that he would consider it \" a great achievement ...","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"if I could unite the country , \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"after decades of increasing partisan polarization in Washington .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"At least 14 House Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"including members of the Congressional Black Caucus ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"boycotted the president ' s address .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Democrats invited about 20 illegal immigrants","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"known as \" Dreamers \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"to attend the speech ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"prompting an objection from a Republican lawmaker","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Capitol police should check IDs","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and arrest anyone in the U.S. illegally .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"As Mr. Trump strode to the Speaker ' s rostrum ,","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"he was in a position","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that any president would relish :","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"riding a strong economy","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that he credited to his slashing of regulations and taxes .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"And the full impact of his tax cuts is about to show up in workers ' paychecks over the next few weeks .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s address underscored the importance of the economy for his party , and for him , in this critical mid-term election year .","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"The president ' s job-approval ratings are still relatively weak","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"( 38 percent in Gallup , 43 percent in Rasmussen ) ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"although voters give him higher marks for his handling of the economy .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Seated in the gallery with first lady Melania Trump were 14 guests of the White House","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"to help illustrate the president ' s themes ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"including a couple","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"who adopted a child","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"suffering from opioid addiction ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and parents of two girls","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"who were murdered by MS-13 , the notorious Central American gang","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that is increasing its U.S. presence","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"because of immigration from its native lands .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The president , with a less combative tone","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"than he often takes on social media ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"told Congress","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that he wanted to discuss \" what kind of future we are going to have , and what kind of nation we are going to be","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"- all of us , together , as one team , one people , and one American family . \"","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"\" Americans love their country , \"","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"\" And they deserve a government","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that shows them the same love and loyalty in return . \"","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"But the president ' s agenda this year","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"- reforming the immigration system ,","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"rebuilding infrastructure","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"and beefing up the military -","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"will be complicated by hardening of partisan lines ahead of the mid-terms .","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"On North Korea , Mr. Trump offered no new prescriptions for the regime of Kim Jong Un and its nuclear weapons .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"North Korea ' s \" reckless pursuit of nuclear missiles could very soon threaten our homeland , \"","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"and vowed to continue a campaign of \" maximum pressure","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"to prevent that from happening. \"","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"The White House invited three guests","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"connected with North Korea","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"- Fred and Cindy Warmbier of Ohio ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"whose son Otto died","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"after being severely injured in custody","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"while studying in that country .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Also in attendance was Ji Seong-ho ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"who escaped North Korea as a starving boy decades ago .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"\" We need only look at the depraved character of the North Korean regime","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"to understand the nature of the nuclear threat","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"it could pose to America and our allies , \"","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"On Iran , Mr. Trump reiterated","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that he is asking the Congress to address \" fundamental flaws in the terrible Iran nuclear deal. \"","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"The president said","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"the threats from rogue regimes , terrorist groups , and rivals such as China and Russia demonstrate the need for a stronger military .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"He called for an end to the \" dangerous defense sequester \" of funds and more money","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to modernize the U.S. nuclear arsenal .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"\" In confronting these dangers ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"we know","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"that weakness is the surest path to conflict ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"and unmatched power is the surest means of our defense , \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"\" As part of our defense , we must modernize and rebuild our nuclear arsenal ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"hopefully never having to use it ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"but making it so strong and powerful","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"that it will deter any acts of aggression . \"","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"He added ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"\" Perhaps someday in the future there will be a magical moment","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"when the countries of the world will get together","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"to eliminate their nuclear weapons .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"Unfortunately , we are not there yet . \"","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"Building on a move","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"he made at the Department of Veterans Affairs last year ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"the president called on Congress to \" empower every Cabinet secretary with the authority","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"to reward good workers","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"- and to remove federal employees","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"who undermine the public trust","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"or fail the American people . \"","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"Mr. Trump also spoke of more funding for vocational training and to reform prisons ,","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"although he offered no specifics .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"In summing up his first year in office ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Mr. Trump told Congress ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"\" The State of our Union is strong","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"because our people are strong . \"","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"The president said of terrorists ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"\" When possible ,","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"we annihilate them .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"When necessary ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"we must be able to detain and question them .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"But we must be clear :","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Terrorists are not merely criminals .","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"They are unlawful enemy combatants .","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"And","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"when captured overseas ,","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"they should be treated like the terrorists","depth":16},{"id":154,"text":"they are . \"","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"Previously , Mr. Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"\" we have foolishly released hundreds of dangerous terrorists ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"only to meet them again on the battlefield","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"- including the ISIS leader , al-Baghdadi . \"","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"Congress must provide \" all necessary power","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"to detain terrorists","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"- wherever we chase them down . \"","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":325,"left":222,"right":324,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":222,"left":171,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":167,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":164,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":165,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":168,"right":169,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":168,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":186,"right":220,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":180,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":177,"right":179,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":172,"right":176,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":11,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":12,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":173,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":178,"right":18,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":182,"right":184,"